                <head>286. Summary of Conclusions of a Policy Review Committee Meeting<note n="1"
                        type="source" xml:id="d286fn1">Source: Carter Library, <persName
                            corresp="#p_BZ_1">Brzezinski</persName> Donated Material, Box 24,
                        Meetings: Policy Review Committee Meetings (<gloss target="#t_PRC_2"
                            >PRC</gloss>), <gloss target="#t_PRC_2">PRC</gloss> 51: 1/26/78. Secret.
                        The meeting took place in the White House Situation Room.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>Washington</placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian"
                            when="1978-01-26">January 26, 1978</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <list type="subject">
                    <head>SUBJECT</head>
                    <item>Management of Arms Transfers</item>
                </list>
                <list type="participants">
                    <head>PARTICIPANTS</head>
                    <item>
